Starbits offstage to confirm into early kills using fair is slept on, imo.

You can only air dodge through it or use up B in the blast zone, which you can't get back to the stage from. It'll often kill their 2nd jump even if the fair doesn't kill.

#SSBU #SSBU_Rosalina https://t.co/cp1Divn2Qm

People might ask, why not just throw out fair from the same distance? People can easily predict the fair and can air dodge through it or go up or down to make it miss, but once the starbits hits, its almost guaranteed to hit, and starbits has a wide range and distance offstage.
久しぶりにこんながらがらなのでみんな来てくださいな
